This Starbucks has AWESOME staff! EVERYONE has a smile, they are always in good mood, with customer service and manners. I love how well this group of young people work together. I have come to often expect this level of customer service from young ladies, but the young men here provide an equally extraordinarily positive experience.  I come in almost every weekday morning and see Kenny always so busy making sure the store is well stocked and things are moving smoothly. BJ and Jamel welcoming customers warmly and take orders so efficiently, while Raina and Delisa make drinks with speed and perfection. Last but certainly not lease Brandon is the best at making sure customers get their orders IN HAND, with a smile and a kind word to send you on your way to fight whatever the work week throws at you. This staff makes you feel so special like their only customer!! I'm proud of these young men and women.

This is a busy Starbucks right outside one of the entrances for L'Efant Plaza metro. The office buildings around this place generate ample foot traffic that I have seen a line of a few people every time I have visited this Starbucks location.  There is limited seating available for a Starbucks as busy as this one and most of them are claimed by folks who are there working and using free Wifi.  My drinks have always been made correctly and the baristas are friendly too.
